@node History_engl

History:

    V1.20 - checksum introduced for reliable data recognition
            -> FORMAT INCOMPATIBLE WITH PRIOR VERSIONS !!
          - data capacity increased three-fold through using
            of green and blue channel, too

    V1.19 - line-length-calculation fixed -> more data capacity
            especially with small picture files

    V1.18 - English ReadMe/Guide
          - English program-version (_no_ Locale-support)
          - automatic line-spacing within "About"-requester introduced
            no topaz/8-limit any more.
          - window-size now always ok (WA_Width/Height replaced
            with WA_InnerWidth/Height)

    V1.17 - Font-representation-bug on wb-font!=topaz/8 eliminated
          - "About"-requester limited on topaz/8 for that version
            to ensure readability on big wb-fonts

    V1.16 - unneccesary AllocAslRequest()s/FreeAslRequest()s removed
          - static path-arrays (for the ASL-requesters) changed into
            dynamic ones -> Executable shrinked from >50K to <17K !

    V1.15 - full-functionality GUI-version

    V1.8  - full-functionality Shell-Version

    V1.1  - first Version



